tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE charging_stations (
  station_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  power_output DECIMAL,
  plug_type VARCHAR(50),
  last_used TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Charging_Usage (
    usage_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    station_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    energy_consumed DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE charging_stations (
  station_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  station_type VARCHAR(50),
  num_of_ports INT,
  last_used TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE vehicle_info (
  vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  make VARCHAR(50),
  model VARCHAR(50),
  year INT,
  owner_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (owner_id) REFERENCES owners(owner_id)
)

CREATE TABLE charging_sessions (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP,
  charged_energy DECIMAL,
  station_id INT,
  vehicle_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (station_id) REFERENCES charging_stations(station_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (vehicle_id) REFERENCES vehicle_info(vehicle_id)
)

CREATE TABLE vehicles (
   vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   vehicle_type VARCHAR(50),
   vehicle_model VARCHAR(50),
   license_plate VARCHAR(20),
   owner_name VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE charging_logs (
   log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   station_id INT,
   vehicle_id INT,
   charging_date TIMESTAMP,
   charging_time INT,
   energy_consumed DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE charging_stations (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  station_name VARCHAR(255),
  location VARCHAR(255),
  power_rating FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE charging_sessions (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  station_id INT,
  vehicle_id INT,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP,
  energy_consumed FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE vehicles (
  vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  make VARCHAR(255),
  model VARCHAR(255),
  year INT,
  battery_capacity FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE stations_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  station_id INT,
  status VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE users (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255),
  email VARCHAR(255),
  phone_number VARCHAR(15)
)
